#!/usr/bin/env testml


*jsc.validate(*json) == *valid


=== Test 1 - valid definition - valid definition schema
--- valid: true
--- jsc
{
  "$ref": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2019-09/schema"
}
--- json
{"$defs": {"foo": {"type": "integer"}}}


=== Test 2 - invalid definition - invalid definition schema
--- valid: false
--- jsc
{
  "$ref": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2019-09/schema"
}
--- json
{"$defs": {"foo": {"type": 1}}}


